data.description: WOW! YOU HAVE TO SEE THIS HOUSE! Beautifully finished hardwood floors, Custom Kitchen Cabinetry (SOFT CLOSE & PULLOUTS), stainless steel app, granite countertops in kitchen & baths, recessed lighting, tiled showers, updated lighting, laundry room with washer/dryer, prof landscaped yard with drip, wood fireplace and brand new garage door!  Boy does the stucco look terrific! Newer windows, newer roof, RING doorbell with security cameras and outside lights!  Did I mention a large enclosed back yard with peek views of the Sandias? This awesome home is TURNKEY! Just bring your suitcases!  Meticulous sellers have gone through every home detail to make sure the house is in tip top shape!  It's a PRIDE thing! Home close to Coronado Mall, Uptown, restaurants & theatre! It's a GEM. Bring offers!!!
